&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interest in Personal Injury Law.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-starter driven by long-term career goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Superior writing and oral advocacy skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
