&lt;p&gt;We are seeking full-time customer service professionals who are passionate about making a difference in people’s lives and committed to delivering an exceptional client experience. As a Case Consultant, you will be the first point of contact for clients facing challenging and often traumatic situations. Your role is pivotal in offering support and reassurance from the moment they reach out to us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Case Control Center operates 7 days a week from 7:00 AM to 9:00 PM PST. This position requires active employment with full weekend availability.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
